  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2817950/extras/d10709b9180dc525b0bfcf81d724b3be.avif?t=1743069409\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2817950/extras_big/d10709b9180dc525b0bfcf81d724b3be.avif?t=1743069409 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Quadrillion – A Thrilling FPS Horror Experience in an Alternate World War I</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>Short Description:</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Immerse yourself in Quadrillion, a pulse-pounding FPS set in a twisted version of World War I. Battle relentless zombie soldiers, monstrous creatures, and supernatural forces in grim trenches and abandoned cities—every step could be your last.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >[ odkaz na wishlist  ]</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2817950/extras/6659784d45ddc66b635201cdcdde616a.avif?t=1743069409\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2817950/extras_big/6659784d45ddc66b635201cdcdde616a.avif?t=1743069409 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>Extended Description:</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to Quadrillion – a unique experience that combines heart-pounding FPS action with the eerie terror of an alternative World War I. Trapped in a nightmarish world where trenches hide deadly secrets and shadowy forces lurk, you must fight against endless waves of undead soldiers, brutal abominations, and inexplicable supernatural phenomena. Navigate through eerie, deserted cities and deformed landscapes as you confront both external horrors and the inner demons that haunt you. Every decision, every move, and every heartbeat counts in your fight for survival. Quadrillion is more than just a game—it’s a journey into the darkest corners of fear. Are you ready to face your worst nightmare?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >[ odkaz na wishlist  ]</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2817950/extras/062dd447b7e6f745a68c03b868d8ed6f.avif?t=1743069409\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2817950/extras_big/062dd447b7e6f745a68c03b868d8ed6f.avif?t=1743069409 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>Quadrillion – Step Into a Living Nightmare</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>About the Game:</strong><br>Quadrillion is a thrilling FPS that plunges you into an alternate version of World War I. In this dark and twisted world, real historical elements merge with imaginative horror to create an immersive and unforgettable experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Why You'll Love It:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Authentic Elements:</strong> Our game features real photographs, promotional posters, period-accurate weapons, and uniforms that ground the experience in history and elevate its authenticity.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Dark and Terrifying Atmosphere:</strong> Experience the dread of grim trenches, abandoned cities, and distorted landscapes where tension is around every corner.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2817950/extras/290da6755ec05ffb22413b6a15f33540.avif?t=1743069409\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2817950/extras_big/290da6755ec05ffb22413b6a15f33540.avif?t=1743069409 width=800 height=450 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>A Story Rooted in Reality and Imagination:</strong> Inspired by true events, our narrative weaves historical facts with creative twists, delivering a unique and compelling storyline.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2817950/extras/a887c1dffe41f359508a90bf99535496.avif?t=1743069409\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2817950/extras_big/a887c1dffe41f359508a90bf99535496.avif?t=1743069409 width=800 height=450 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Immersive Sound Design:</strong> Bone-chilling soundscapes are intricately woven into the gameplay, pulling you deeper into the horror of the trenches.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The Protagonist’s Nightmare:</strong> The entire game unfolds as a vivid nightmare of the main character—a surreal journey where personal fears and the horrors of war collide.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Step into Quadrillion and prepare to face the darkest depths of fear.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >[ odkaz na wishlist  ]</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2817950/extras/8a3f8f5ae55f7444cf69905c6ce029b9.avif?t=1743069409\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2817950/extras_big/8a3f8f5ae55f7444cf69905c6ce029b9.avif?t=1743069409 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>Conclusion:</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Although our team consists of only two solitary soldiers, we are determined to see this battle through to a victorious end. We deeply appreciate your support and will keep you regularly informed about the game’s development and upcoming events. Together, we will overcome every obstacle and create an unforgettable experience. Thank you for joining us on this journey!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
